image_analysis.description: A scanned page from a book or report, featuring a collage of seven photographs with corresponding captions related to Jeffrey Epstein. The images include portraits of Epstein with others, a jail cell, a courthouse scene, an aerial view of a building, an aerial view of an island, and a screenshot of a sex offender registry entry. A document identifier is visible at the bottom right.
image_analysis.layout: A multi-panel collage layout with images and text blocks distributed across the page. Each image is accompanied by a caption explaining its context.
